title: Pralay the Destroyer
subTitle: Some thugs annihilate an entire family and flee the scene without facing any consequences. Years later, the universe balances the scales of justice through the sole survivor of the tragedy.

title: Tarla
subTitle: With dreams bigger than every social barrier known to women, Tarla Dalal embarks on an inspirational journey to change the country's culinary landscape.

title: Ramayana
subTitle: Prince Rama embarks on a daring mission to save his kidnapped wife Sita from the evil Ravana. Aided by his loyal brother Lakshmana and an army of monkeys, Rama faces difficult challenges in his journey to Lanka.

subTitle: Suspicion turns to obsession when a man starts to think that an oddball neighbor killed a 5-year-old girl.

title: Phone Bhoot
subTitle: Inspired by stories from their childhood, two young men create a business around capturing ghosts. However, their endeavour turns dangerous when they must fulfil their promise to a poltergeist.

subTitle: A conservative villager hates the idea of his son relocating to Russia for a job. However, when his son brings a robot to care for him, he develops an unlikely bond with the machine.

title: Crew
subTitle: Three ambitious female cabin attendants from Mumbai get caught in a web of lies during their pursuit of dreams, leading to an unexpected heist.

title: Karan Arjun
subTitle: Karan and Arjun, two brothers driven by revenge, are murdered by their uncle while seeking justice for their father's death. However, they resurrect years later to settle their unfinished score.

title: RRR
subTitle: A fearless revolutionary and an officer in the British force, who once shared a deep bond, decide to join forces and chart out an inspirational path of freedom against the despotic rulers.

title: Deep Sea Python
subTitle: Fisherman Chen Yue and photographer Zhong Ming must set aside their differences after being attacked by a sea creature in the middle of the ocean.

title: Deep Sea Python
subTitle: Fisherman Chen Yue and photographer Zhong Ming must set aside their differences after being attacked by a sea creature in the middle of the ocean.

title: Gangster
subTitle: Simran, who relocates to Seoul, is distraught when Daya, a gangster, re-enters her life. She has to make a choice between him and her lover Akash, who is a singer at an Indian restaurant.

title: Khamoshi
subTitle: A young woman, who is unable to hear and speak, attempts to save herself when a killer appears at her doorstep.

subTitle: Aditya, Joe, Kedar and Rob form a rock band but break up when they fail to succeed. They lead regular lives until deciding to reunite and take another shot at fulfilling their dreams.

title: 50 Days of Love
subTitle: A gynaecologist reluctantly gets married to a simple woman. However, things take a drastic turn when they both start getting to know each other and uncover the lies they fed one another.

title: Sandwich
subTitle: Sher Singh has two wives, Nisha and Sweety, and juggles his time between them. However, when his two wives cross paths, his troubles increase manifold leading to hilarious situations.

title: Aitraaz
subTitle: When a company chairman's trophy wife stirs up a storm in a happily married employee's life, the tumultuous winds drag all of them into an intense courtroom showdown.

title: Aranmanai 4
subTitle: Suspicious about his sister's death, Saravanan, a lawyer, tries to solve the mystery behind it, only to discover a mysteriously dark force at play.

title: Baaghi
subTitle: Determined to rescue his former love, the ruggedly handsome Ronny confronts his enemies with a flurry of powerful roundhouse kicks and bone-crushing punches.

title: Sooryavanshi
subTitle: With the looming threat of a terrorist attack on Mumbai, ATS chief Sooryavanshi embarks on a mission to hunt for 600 kgs of missing RDX and the conspiring perpetrators.

title: Spyder
subTitle: Shiva, an intelligence officer, develops a phone software that helps him track those in need of help. He sets out to save the people of Hyderabad when he realises that a serial killer is on the loose.

title: Farrey
subTitle: Brought up in an orphanage, child prodigy Niyati gets admitted into a prestigious school. Soon, surrounded by money, she gets engulfed in a cheating racket.

title: Bhoot Returns
subTitle: Tarun and Namrata move into a luxurious bungalow with Taman and Nimmi, their son and daughter respectively. However, strange occurrences start taking place and they must escape in order to survive.

subTitle: Scientist Jennifer Ashgrove is overworked and decides to take a retreat to the countryside with her husband in the hopes of mending their strained relationship.

title: Fillers
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of promotional videos and trailers of Bollywood movies featuring popular actors and actresses.

title: Lakshya
subTitle: Karan, an aimless young man, joins the Indian Army on a whim but backs out when he finds a soldier's life to be difficult. When this creates conflict with his girlfriend, he rejoins to make her proud.

title: Race 3
subTitle: The thirst for power drives a wealthy family to become rivals in a risky heist. As a consequence, they face betrayal and danger along the way.

title: Krack
subTitle: Three delinquents attempt to outwit a resolute police officer, underestimating his clever methods and unwavering dedication to law enforcement.

title: Badal
subTitle: Badal's family dies at the hands of a corrupt police officer. While he is raised by his father's friend, he turns into a terrorist and vows to avenge his family's death.

title: Toilet: Ek Prem Katha
subTitle: Jaya marries Keshav but is disappointed to learn that there is no toilet in his house. As a result, he tries to pacify her with temporary arrangements.

title: Chakra Ka Rakshak
subTitle: A police officer and soldier team up and decide to end the cybercriminals that pose a threat to the safety of people on the Internet.
